
1. Incase of a fire people should exit the building using the shown fire exits on a line. 
2. Incase of any saftey threat, you should always ensure your own safety first.
3. Beware of the different fire exstingishers available and which to use when.
4. if there is a fire and you are inside a room, the best way to get out is by laying on the ground and crawling out.
5. After everyone is out of the rooms, and at the fire assembly point ensure to take a rollcall.
